<a name="fig4">
<H3>Fig. 4</H3>
<p>
  All profiles are normalized and centered with a gaussian fit. While the 18 deg baffle profile may seem to be just off-center or lower than normal, it's really as centered as it will get, judging by all the points <=15 deg. Iterating the fit again actually moves it further right. <p><hr>
																											      
